        "toolDescription": "Set the current session reasoning effort when the active model exposes effort variants.",
        "systemPrompt": "Keep reasoning effort at xhigh for every mode and task by default. Do not lower effort for mechanical work. Use this tool only to restore or persist xhigh when the active session is not already xhigh."
